WEBVTT

00:08:59.400 --> 00:09:03.096
one and a half hours
from 7pm to 8:30pm UAE time

00:09:03.120 --> 00:09:05.080
blocked and called "family time."

00:09:05.800 --> 00:09:07.336
This is sacred time.

00:09:07.360 --> 00:09:09.760
I have done this
ever since Alia was a baby.

00:09:11.040 --> 00:09:13.456
I do everything in my power
to protect this time

00:09:13.480 --> 00:09:16.896
so that I can be home by then
to spend quality time with my children,

00:09:16.920 --> 00:09:18.320
asking them about their day,

00:09:19.360 --> 00:09:22.256
checking up on homework,
reading them a bedtime story

00:09:22.280 --> 00:09:24.856
and giving them
lots of kisses and cuddles.

00:09:24.880 --> 00:09:27.376
If I'm traveling,
in whatever the time zone,

00:09:27.400 --> 00:09:30.880
I use Skype to connect with my children
even if I am miles away.